â€¢ Youngerâ€™s Domain ğŸ¯ â€” After Sprint, Younger typically applies only to: (1) ongoing criminal prosecutions, (2) certain civil enforcement actions akin to criminal prosecution, and (3) civil proceedings that uniquely further a courtâ€™s judicial functions (e.g., contempt).
